snippet.title: Clutchtime™: Basketball Deckbuilder trailer
snippet.description:
Clutchtime™ is a basketball themed deck building game. Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2995450/Clutchtime_Basketball_Deckbuilder/

The game has two modes: single elimination tournaments with roguelike mechanics and regular season where you can lose some games and still qualify into the playoffs.

Trailer music by Logan Nickleson.
